long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
GoSet is a time tracker for your daily work. It can create time sheets in various formats including CSV, JSON and PDF. What makes GoSet different from other tools is, it works completely offline. 

If you are looking for a minimal and beautiful time tracker, GoSet is right for you.
